    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that:</p> <ul> <li> it is Congress's duty to uphold the U.S. Constitution and all of the fundamental rights, including the freedom of the press; </li> <li> the President must immediately acknowledge his support of the First Amendment and express his support for U.S. democracy; </li> <li> the United States should continue being a democracy, not an autocracy; </li> <li> White House spokespersons should not issue fake news; and </li> <li> White House spokespersons who offer alternative or inaccurate facts should retract their statements immediately.</li> </ul>]]></text>
